OL,3,CRail workers to strike in dispute over
OL,4,Csafety of trains
OL,6,FWorkers at East Midlands Railway (EMR)
OL,7,Fare to strike in a dispute over safety.
OL,9,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,10,FTransport union (RMT) will walk out on
OL,11,F1 August.
OL,13,FThe union said it has been in dispute
OL,14,Fwith EMR since April, claiming there
OL,15,Fare problems with some trains.
OL,17,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,18,Fsaid: "RMT is demanding that while
OL,19,Ffaults exist and until these trains
OL,20,Fare shown to be operating properly,
OL,21,Fthey should be taken out of service."
OL,26,@zD@GOU}D@eO]
