OL,3,CRail workers to strike in dispute over
OL,4,Csafety of trains
OL,6,FAn East Midlands Railway spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid, "Any suggestion that the Hitachi
OL,8,FRail Class 810 fleet does not meet the
OL,9,Frequired safety standards is
OL,10,Fincorrect. These trains entered
OL,11,Fpassenger service only after
OL,12,Fsuccessfully completing all required
OL,13,Ftesting and meeting the rigorous
OL,14,Fsafety standards required by the
OL,15,Findependent regulator.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
