OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784735286
OL,3,CRail workers to strike in dispute over
OL,4,Csafety of trains
OL,6,F"We recognise the Class 810 fleet has
OL,7,Fencountered performance and
OL,8,Freliability issues in service and are
OL,9,Fworking with the manufacturer, Hitachi
OL,10,FRail, to resolve these issues as
OL,11,Fquickly as possible.
OL,13,F"EMR continues to engage in
OL,14,Fdiscussions with RMT regarding this
OL,15,Fdispute."
